# MR GIFT - Gift Giving Platform

A modern gift-giving platform with React frontend and Flask backend.

## Project Structure
```
mr-gift-clean/
├── frontend/          # React + Vite app
├── backend/           # Flask API
└── README.md
```

## Quick Start

### Frontend
```bash
cd frontend
npm install
npm run dev
```

### Backend  
```bash
cd backend
pip install -r requirements.txt
python app.py
```

## Deployment
- Frontend: Vercel (auto-deployed)
- Backend: Railway/Render

## Environment Variables
Copy `.env.example` files and add your keys:
- Clerk: Authentication
- Stripe: Payments
